title: RENOVATED FURNISHED IN ONE HOTEL SOBE RONEY!!
posting_body: ['Complete renovation completed in 2021.', 'Meticulously designed 2 bedroom plus Den with customized Armazen kitchen, Bosch Appliances, built ins, open kitchen, spa like bathrooms.', 'Large terrace with unobstructed West, North and South view.', 'Includes Basic cable, wifi and water.', 'Roney residents have access to all the 1 Hotel Amenities, including 3 ocean front pools, hot tub, beach services.', 'On-site restaurants include Habitat, STK, Plnthouse organic cafe, Watr at the rooftop and more!', 'Home to Soul Cycle, Anatomy Gym, high end spa and retail fashion boutiques.', 'Valet and full-time security', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
